      <title>FTX 质疑向前雇员出售欧盟资产的交易已经完成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/ftx-disputes-the-sale-of-eu-assets-to-ex-employees-is-complete</link>
      <description><![CDATA[关于谁拥有 Sam Bankman-Fried 的前加密企业的欧洲子公司的问题似乎已经得到解决：总部位于迪拜的 Backpack Exchange 表示，经过数月的争论，它已经收购了 FTX EU。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/ftx-disputes-the-sale-of-eu-assets-to-ex-employees-is-complete</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 03:19:16 GMT</pubDate>
