    <item>
      <title>拜登将进一步限制 Nvidia AI 芯片出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/biden-to-further-limit-nvidia-amd-ai-chip-exports-in-final-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登的政府计划在离任前几天对英伟达等公司的人工智能芯片出口实施新一轮限制，这是他为防止先进技术落入中国和俄罗斯手中而采取的最后一项措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/biden-to-further-limit-nvidia-amd-ai-chip-exports-in-final-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 21:36:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约市试图通过加薪来结束 Uber、Lyft 司机停工现象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/nyc-is-trying-to-end-uber-lyft-driver-lockouts-with-a-pay-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市正试图通过一系列新措施来堵塞 Uber Technologies Inc. 和 Lyft Inc. 用来拒绝向司机支付数百万美元工资的漏洞，这些措施实际上将使司机的工资提高约 6.1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/nyc-is-trying-to-end-uber-lyft-driver-lockouts-with-a-pay-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 21:06:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
